snippet.title: Car Mayhem - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
One of many shovelware games from Sabec Limited, the same company who made the terrible 3D remake of the Popeye arcade game.

This one has three games in one: a crappy police chase game, a crappy Destruction Derby mode and a boring zombie mode that makes Carmageddon 64 more satisfying. And again, Unity Asset Store stuff all over the place.

Car Madness (C) Sabed Limited
Also available on Nintendo Switch.
